n style=\"color: red;\">堅持人強馬壯 提防中計 相信兄弟 各自爬山 和理非見到勇武手足做嘢 唔該開遮幫佢哋擋鏡頭 例如被恐襲 有狗混入及偷拍</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">《緊急廣傳》由其唔上連登位置<br />\n有好多兄弟買左迪卡儂 但唔記得所有產品入面有RFID！<br />\n記得剪牌🙏記得剪牌🙏記得剪牌</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">失物追蹤聯絡，失主記得問對方入面有咩先好接觸，免被恐怖騎劫，找回失物記得通知我刪除</span></strong><br />\n7.21 上環 - <a href=\"https://t.me/UID1157624\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FUID1157624&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGd34HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=c635907c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/UID1157624</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BiVuQ12.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBiVuQ12.png&h=f5d53396&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>將呢條恐怖份子滲透香港歷史詳述散去全世界</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190727/59867771\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190727%2F59867771&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGd34HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=7c5a0918\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190727%2F59867771&h=2d97df16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190727/59867771</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">[URGENT] 我要攬炒🙏Like🙏Subscribe🙏Follow🙏Retweet</span></strong><br />\nFacebook:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standwithhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandwithhk&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGd34HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=9596796f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standwithhk</a><br />\nTwitter:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Stand_with_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStand_with_HK&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGd34HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=1ad848ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Stand_with_HK</a><br />\nInstagram:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/standwithhk_\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fstandwithhk_&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGd34HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=8f5ec197\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/standwithhk_</a><br />\nYouTube:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCyi42Y5o1ksO_yFItyHW7Jw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCyi42Y5o1ksO_yFItyHW7Jw&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGd34HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=ec5b4268\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCyi42Y5o1ksO_yFItyHW7Jw</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">傳說7.21恐怖份子黑社會圖上武器之一<br />\n7.27香港人不站出來追究<br />\n這種恐怖襲擊將會在18區無處不在</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">中聯辦背後策劃證據</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.rfa/videos/vb.454004001340790/694413694332018/?type=2&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcantonese.rfa%2Fvideos%2Fvb.454004001340790%2F694413694332018%2F%3Ftype%3D2%26theater&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGd34HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=c62d2d23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.rfa/videos/vb.454004001340790/694413694332018/?type=2&amp;theater</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sUx81OM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsUx81OM.png&h=2ee50185&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n🎆光復香港🎆時代革命🎆爭取五大訴求🎆<br />\n📢1. 全面撤回送中條例<br />\n📢2. 撤銷6.12暴動定性&nbsp;<br />\n📢3. 釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究&nbsp;<br />\n📢4. 全面實行雙普選&nbsp;<br />\n📢5. 成立獨立調查委員會，追究黑警濫用暴力，徹查警黑勾結7.21元朗恐襲<br />\n<strong>7.28 14:00 最後底線，否則行動升級</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">睇到最底 內容包括：「運動時間」 「聯署」 《會加入新聯署 記得去簽》 白宮需要係電郵內確認先叫完成 記得係電郵㩒連結 唔好懶 所有活動必須同時進行</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">持續不合作運動「兄弟爬山，各自努力」<